Key changes:
1. Removed all `theme="dark"` props from all components in the second section
2. Added light background and text colors if needed (depending on your CSS)
3. Changed the logo from white to black if available (you may need to adjust the logo path)

If your `styles.main` class already has specific styling for light mode, you might not need to add explicit background and text colors.
